  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "Changing the values of gas and gasMultiplier in `hardhat.config.js` file  are not taking effect. The smart contract deployment is always done using the hardhat default values.\r\n\r\n**Config 1**\r\n````quote\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  solidity: \"0.7.3\",\r\n  networks: {\r\n    ropsten: {\r\n      url: `https://ropsten.infura.io/v3/${INFURA_PROJECT_ID}`,\r\n      accounts: [`0x${ROPSTEN_PRIVATE_KEY}`],\r\n      gasMultiplier: 2\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n````\r\n**Config 2**\r\n````quote\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  solidity: \"0.7.3\",\r\n  networks: {\r\n    ropsten: {\r\n      url: `https://ropsten.infura.io/v3/${INFURA_PROJECT_ID}`,\r\n      accounts: [`0x${ROPSTEN_PRIVATE_KEY}`],\r\n      gas: 500000\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n````",
